This is for nexell linux Crosstools (ARM)

	1. make "crosstools" directory in "/opt"

	2. change directory permission "chmod 666 /opt/crosstools"

	3. uncompress arm-cortex_a9-eabi-4.7-eglibc-2.18.tar.gz in "/opt/crosstools"

	4. set crosstools PATH in shell or in '.bashrc'
		-> export PATH=$PATH:/opt/crosstools/arm-cortex_a9-eabi-4.7-eglibc-2.18/bin

This is for nexell linux Crosstools (ARM64)

	1. make "crosstools" directory in "/opt"

	2. change directory permission "chmod 666 /opt/crosstools"

	3. uncompress gcc-linaro-4.9-2014.11-x86_64_aarch64-linux-gnu.tar.gz in "/opt/crosstools"

	4. set crosstools PATH in shell or in '.bashrc'
		-> export PATH=$PATH:/opt/crosstools/gcc-linaro-4.9-2014.11-x86_64_aarch64-linux-gnu/bin
		
